claim.claim-text:
10. The process which comprises: 
providing a composite laminate having an outer film layer with an inner surface and an outer surface opposed to said inner surface, an inner plastic layer bonded to said inner surface, and a colored, decorative layer on said outer surface; 
reinforcing the composite laminate with a first, innermost reinforcing material bonded to the inner plastic layer; 
further reinforcing the composite laminate with a second outermost reinforcing material bonded to the inner surface of the outer film layer between the first reinforcing material and the outer film layer which prevents the first reinforcing material from being visible through the colored layer.
